                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Hunter</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Guatemala</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1900-03-29">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 29, 1900</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Hunter reports that the Guatemalan Government replies, in connection with
                    Department’s cablegram of the 28th instant, that Minister Arriaga has full power
                    to grant the requested extension.</p>
                <p>The Guatemalan Government, on the 22d instant, furnished the legation with a copy
                    of its memorial, which was acknowledged on the 24th instant.</p>
                <p>British minister has been furnished with Department’s cable instruction.)</p>
            </div>
        </body>
